{"tid":1669674,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"正視聽。智利其實未贏。","createTime":"2019-10-22T16:47:20.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-23T10:48:13.000Z","uid":307180,"like":10,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"bf2f33927707193eede5043915de9de373049749","tid":1669674,"uid":307180,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-22T16:47:20.000Z","msg":"利申我都唔算知好多所以長話短說。<br />\n<br />\n發現好多人以為智利人純粹因為公共交通加價而示威、燒車。但其實智利同香港一樣，背後仲有好多原因搞到今時今日咁。<br />\n<br />\n例如教育廢得黎又好q貴，醫療系統好差，人工好低但物價過高等等，好多唔公平唔fair既政策，先造成今日咁激烈既衝突。<br />\n<br />\n雖然智利人好strong好癲好愛抱不平，但都唔係單單因為地鐵加價就一野去到咁盡。其實同香港好似，<ins><strong>正如你都唔會想睇到外媒話林鄭撤回左條例就係贏左一樣</strong></ins>，我地都唔好再吹奏佢地贏左。一齊努力了解下佢地既狀況。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />共勉之。<br />\n<br />\n係twitter copy左啲佢地既文宣。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/1HsJKfQ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F1HsJKfQ.jpg&h=3375b692&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/jp2mvVP.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fjp2mvVP.jpg&h=7dcbd0af&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/wGxapfO.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FwGxapfO.jpg&h=807329ab&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/jGLrG2s.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FjGLrG2s.jpg&h=06f30524&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/wGxapfO.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FwGxapfO.jpg&h=807329ab&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: gold;\">[size=10]光復香港<br />\n時代革命[/size=10]</span></strong>"},{"pid":"65bd16d5a09043782229f1f0a1c7ca8b2967b88f","tid":1669674,"uid":34293,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-22T16:48:09.000Z","msg":"日積月累  邊可能咁易解決"},{"pid":"38ca8a24e85ebad9e9eebb4cb395ab20907372b6","tid":1669674,"uid":307180,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"cited